{"tid":1698614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[英國connect] 星期日係國殤紀念日，一齊紀念為我哋奮戰過嘅英軍！","createTime":"2019-11-07T15:17:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T05:59:53.000Z","uid":91721,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6cecf80566a6d7a556213e9a9bdd74ec85571454","tid":1698614,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:17:04.000Z","msg":"【 和平紀念日悼念儀式 Remembrance Day 】<br />\nThis Sunday marks the Remembrance Sunday, the day to remember the fallen servicemen and women who died in the line of duty. At 10:45 am, a multi-faith memorial service will be held at the Cenotaph in Central. Don&rsquo;t forget your remembrance poppy to commemorate the military personnel who have died in war. Lest We Forget. <br />\n<br />\n星期日是國殤紀念日，香港退伍軍人聯會將於星期日上午十時四十五分在中環和平紀念碑舉行聯合宗教悼念活動。歡迎各位市民出席，佩戴紅色的虞美人花一同悼念在戰爭中犧牲的軍人。永誌不忘。<br />\n<br />\n#Lestweforget #Armistice #Armistice100 #remembrance #remebranceday #HongKong #wewillrememberthem #ww1 #wearapoppy"},{"pid":"5e74989f1b9d924b9a8203c1b5ebf382fda74c94","tid":1698614,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:35:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"166cf6936980b8cf60a12f16a3ea41423f2f7e9c","tid":1698614,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T16:25:04.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"01e53c2e446e62be7f4180875f91c9a06972a604","tid":1698614,"uid":32204,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T16:26:12.000Z","msg":"當年香港人(香港義勇軍)、加拿大人同印度人都為香港流過血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb1dd9b60e55ed78fe9b018c1a98fb5f77850444","tid":1698614,"uid":91721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"01e53c2e446e62be7f4180875f91c9a06972a604","tid":1698614,"uid":32204,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T16:26:12.000Z","msg":"當年香港人(香港義勇軍)、加拿大人同印度人都為香港流過血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T23